" bind a key to toggle gundo window
nnoremap <C-g> :GundoToggle<CR>

" use jj for easy esc
imap jj <Esc>

" use enter to create blank line
map <Enter> o<ESC>
map <S-Enter> O<ESC>

" show a visual line under the cursor's current line
set cursorline

